Dear W 2026 TIM Project Team, good evening!
You now have access to TIM Project and Thesis Completion (TIM PTC), the dig=
ital resource I use to support students develop strong TIM projects that ad=
d value to their clients. You will retain access throughout the Winter term=
.
First Deliverable and Due Date
Your first deliverable is the TIM Project Report Start. The deadline is Wed=
nesday January, 7, 11:59 PM.
How to Access TIM PTC

  1.
Log into Brightspace.
  2.
Select =93Resource.=94
  3.
Choose TIM Project and Thesis Completion.

Inside TIM PTC, you can:

  *
Follow the full project schedule.
  *
Upload all six report deliverables and your G1 slide decks.
  *
Review recently completed TIM projects.
  *
Access detailed guidelines for every chapter of your report.
  *
Use curated ChatGPT prompts to support your work.
  *
And much more.

To get started, please review the module titled:
=93Schedule & Notes" Winter 2026 TIM Projects
Please let me know immediately if you encounter issues/errors/incomplete pa=
rts, contradictions on the TIM PTC pages or have suggestions on how to impr=
ove them. I will fix or improve the resource quickly.
________________________________
I=92m excited to work with each of you this Winter and to support you in pr=
oducing excellent TIM project reports that add value to real clients.
Once again =97 welcome aboard!
Warm regards,
Tony B.


